RetroArch Instructions:
Place both .cfg and .png with matching names in your RetroArch overlay directory.
Rename the "Config.cfg" to match the filename of your ROM. Place this file inside the core's config folder. 
Need help finding these directories? Full support is available at https://mroverlay.org/setup

Batocera Instructions:
Ensure both the ".PNG" and ".INFO" filenames match the name of your ROM filename. Place both these files in the "/share/decorations/games" directory (create the "games" folder if it doesn't exist already).